  "title": "Class 4 Driver (Logistics / HSA)",
  "description": "<p>Job description:</p><p>We are seeking a reliable and detail-oriented Delivery & Logistics Specialist to manage the daily transport of goods, equipment, and materials. This role is critical to maintaining our supply chain efficiency and ensuring customer satisfaction.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Transportation & Delivery:</strong> Execute scheduled daily routes for the collection and delivery of materials, goods, and equipment.</li><li><strong>Load Management:</strong> Oversee and perform the secure loading and unloading of items, ensuring they are properly braced and protected to prevent damage during transit.</li><li><strong>Safety & Compliance:</strong> Adhere to all traffic laws and safety regulations. Maintain a clean driving record and follow company-specific safety protocols for handling heavy or hazardous materials.</li><li><strong>Communication:</strong> Coordinate with dispatchers and warehouse teams to optimize routes and provide real-time updates on delivery status or delays.</li></ul><p><strong>Required Skills & Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Licensing:</strong> Valid Class 4 License</li><li><strong>Time Management:</strong> Proven ability to manage tight schedules and navigate efficiently in various traffic and weather conditions.</li></ul><p>Job Type: Full-time</p><p>Work Location: In person</p>",
