    "description": "<p>Founded in 2017, Beecruit is a manpower solutions company empowered by holistic cloud automation to streamline recruitment and HR processes. As the workforce becomes increasingly demanding, complex and unpredictable, organisations are always on the constant lookout for talents to increase productivity and accelerate innovation to remain competitive and relevant. Through our comprehensive suite of services, we help organisations across different industries to plan and implement recruitment initiatives to meet a diverse range of talent-related challenges. Apart from manpower solutions, we are also capable of projects and events management with a huge database for casual labours. Our experience and expertise ensure we can deliver impactful results for your organisation.</p>\n",
